{"tid":546593,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"【一圖一路】兩年十二次旅行經歷［每日更新，有自爆相］","createTime":"2018-01-31T16:02:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-01T11:17:12.000Z","uid":57013,"like":33,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"1891bec08d0c473e5b858c2b99107b667f8b77e2","tid":546593,"uid":57013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T16:02:44.000Z","msg":"過去兩年都喺做Freelancer為主，一Break無Job做就去旅行<br />\n雖然無乜去好遠好偏嘅地方（因為要同客保持聯絡）<br />\n但都體驗左幾種唔同嘅旅行方式，唔喺啲咩專業旅行家，純粹分享下<br />\n每日出一圖寫一篇短文"},{"pid":"d98eb38293dfaa7a37db67e664ae7b338766bc66","tid":546593,"uid":57013,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T16:04:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/01/000412_29e39d61d0f15f65a75ed8857b00fcd4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F01%2F000412_29e39d61d0f15f65a75ed8857b00fcd4.jpg&h=19c31339&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n／搭順風車（攔便車）的樂趣／<br />\n<br />\n台灣旅行最正嘅地方，喺你可以放心一個人獨遊，去到民風淳樸嘅台東，喺主要道路上隨手舉紙牌，五分鐘內保證有車停低載你。<br />\n伍樓青年旅舍嘅阿子話，如果十分鐘內無車停低，那你要檢討一下樣子了。<br />\n下次再同你地分享我攔便車嘅經歷。<br />\n（紙牌乃本人親筆墨寶）"},{"pid":"0eb172d7c815ba7a7fd243888a334afd815bb7fe","tid":546593,"uid":57013,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T16:27:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ptc3fyg1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fptc3fyg1&h=3c048d57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/1rjvo9mn\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F1rjvo9mn&h=a81c0907&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/tzvp9ufg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ftzvp9ufg&h=a2082cbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n／每年《帶住長老去旅行》都是一個陰謀／<br />\n<br />\n「魔界」是長白山北坡的一道溫泉，由天池上流下瀉，在冰封的山脈中常年不結冰的一道奇景。<br />\n<br />\n一月是我設定好每年《帶住長老去旅行》的固定出發季節，今年來到第三季，家中兩老已經由不太關心變得自動自覺追問行程😛<br />\n<br />\n我心裡暗爽，每年固定一月帶兩老出發，是因為相信人有慣性，你每天早上都飲咖啡，習慣後每早起床就會有咖啡的衝動。<br />\n<br />\n本來兩老不是很愛出門，我的陰謀就是讓他們習慣每年年尾要申請假期、要上網看當地資訊，每年都有這樣一個出發的期待。<br />\n<br />\n第三次《帶住長老去旅行》的目的地在哈爾濱，這次來到了鄰接朝鮮的長白山「魔界」風景區，這裡比雪谷雪鄉都還要冷，感覺像去到零下-40度，相機的電量也瞬間耗了一顆又一顆，手指腳趾分別凍得狠狠地發痛表示要凍壞，連碰一下相機都作痛，我開始後悔這裡並不是適合帶長老來旅行的地方。但奇幻風景在眼前，一痛一痛也要Set好腳架拍照。"},{"pid":"986de76e104246ae75bf7341f041bc19cbcbed67","tid":546593,"uid":25052,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T16:30:28.000Z","msg":"LM<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有睇開你啲片同facebook page <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"043b2d6b921bb95a4a53354879a57e98403182c3","tid":546593,"uid":25086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T16:47:17.000Z","msg":"長白山好似好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60c296b559a137ca789d6cbdbfd66786cda31e11","tid":546593,"uid":57013,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T11:38:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/gqwlof1a\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fgqwlof1a&h=3b8ca518&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/qp6s1yzk\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fqp6s1yzk&h=3f8b5ff5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/e6woqhzp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fe6woqhzp&h=5b64d8a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n拜城(Pai)，亦稱擺鎮、拜縣，是有「泰國小瑞士」美譽的山中小鎮，可見其風光優美聞名。泰國北方一直是被忽略的秘地，看慣了曼谷、芭堤雅的城市和海灘之後，建議你安排一下清邁以及湄宏順府(Mae Hong Son)以東北的Pai為行程，街上有文青風的咖啡館，和當地設計師商店，感受不一樣的泰國。<br />\n<br />\nLove Strawberry Pai是經歷兩個多小時車程後，到達Pai的第一個景點，滿滿的Starberry和心心讓人覺得不知道為何，Strawberry和Love就連上了關係，園裡有多個打卡拍照的Starberry裝置，以及像童年一樣的農莊山景，雖然我對在泰國找Strawberry感到一點疑惑，但成雙成對來到這裡，確有「莓」不醉人人自醉之感。"},{"pid":"ac03dbf21a15ee77581e3d2117a939cd878a1daa","tid":546593,"uid":35780,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T11:57:09.000Z","msg":"都唔知點解旅行要去得遠先算係旅行"},{"pid":"6f7b60ee0f0832ebe49ea7a677c2518eaa4eec89","tid":546593,"uid":78571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T11:58:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edbd2f59525c74e7c0bf65c796bdeacb83cdb917","tid":546593,"uid":57013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac03dbf21a15ee77581e3d2117a939cd878a1daa","tid":546593,"uid":35780,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T11:57:09.000Z","msg":"都唔知點解旅行要去得遠先算係旅行"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T12:15:56.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n其實有唔同嘅經歷就已經喺好好嘅體驗<br />\n<br />\nBtw 一條友單車旅行真喺好爽"},{"pid":"4c4c7405f78dfe84cf9bd8193cbbfe96e20a8ed1","tid":546593,"uid":11776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T18:48:17.000Z","msg":"相唔錯 留名"},{"pid":"a47e7f50c0297e1d3064df3adadbce3074484b97","tid":546593,"uid":148939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T01:18:25.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n等你快啲出post"},{"pid":"d43d83198cac89b591a6116bf5a43cb6c036a1ec","tid":546593,"uid":57013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"986de76e104246ae75bf7341f041bc19cbcbed67","tid":546593,"uid":25052,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T16:30:28.000Z","msg":"LM<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有睇開你啲片同facebook page <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T02:36:33.000Z","msg":"有興趣可以follow埋ig，入面有少少唔同<br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/travelwhencry\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Ftravelwhencry&d=J%2BGjt9OVN8jpNQuOpJCvz2i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=eaee3f19\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/travelwhencry</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d040bdac1089b0fd05a924ff429a6fc5f3262c2","tid":546593,"uid":57013,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T02:37:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/9gv15nt0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F9gv15nt0&h=6af8dbab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/32g0yq9i\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F32g0yq9i&h=c736eb1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/i6g9uwdn\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fi6g9uwdn&h=072e6f47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/q1rw0d6u\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fq1rw0d6u&h=7d3de08f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/5rlxwgts\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F5rlxwgts&h=d363d0a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/6its54wl\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F6its54wl&h=c9e91393&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n泰北接壤寮國和緬甸，和泰南最大分別在於這裡並沒有海，也許讓你覺得和印象中的泰國很不一樣，不過優美的山景讓Pai洋溢了慵散和寫意的情緒，我當年住的Accommodation也是這樣，竹籬圍起的小房子，由禾稈草鋪起的天幕和露天浴池，分明就是一踏足就不願意再走出來的房子別墅。<br />\nP.S. 不過剛好那天熱水不夠，浸了一個涼涼的浸浴。"},{"pid":"826cc6641cc38bc43f91bb400260e573c9d068eb","tid":546593,"uid":126367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"edbd2f59525c74e7c0bf65c796bdeacb83cdb917","tid":546593,"uid":57013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac03dbf21a15ee77581e3d2117a939cd878a1daa","tid":546593,"uid":35780,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T11:57:09.000Z","msg":"都唔知點解旅行要去得遠先算係旅行"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T12:15:56.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n其實有唔同嘅經歷就已經喺好好嘅體驗<br />\n<br />\nBtw 一條友單車旅行真喺好爽"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T02:43:05.000Z","msg":"1月頭一支公去左台灣13日<br />\n由台北，去台中，台南，高雄，順住台鐵落去，正<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62acb9cd5f267e6dfec0130e8cfaf73fad81a4da","tid":546593,"uid":25969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T02:43:49.000Z","msg":"快呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd2170640656390ae383aeb6be40b3e8fc7c7946","tid":546593,"uid":25052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d43d83198cac89b591a6116bf5a43cb6c036a1ec","tid":546593,"uid":57013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"986de76e104246ae75bf7341f041bc19cbcbed67","tid":546593,"uid":25052,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T16:30:28.000Z","msg":"LM<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有睇開你啲片同facebook page <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T02:36:33.000Z","msg":"有興趣可以follow埋ig，入面有少少唔同<br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/travelwhencry\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Ftravelwhencry&d=J%2BGjt9OVN8jpNQuOpJCvz2i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=eaee3f19\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/travelwhencry</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T03:57:17.000Z","msg":"好,一陣follow<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05783aa81f411dc5368e9b54a0e003494c195b83","tid":546593,"uid":57013,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T06:52:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/nl1dcwhu\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fnl1dcwhu&h=09ae26c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/q6xb83c7\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fq6xb83c7&h=dd1ee802&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/onwb1gq6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fonwb1gq6&h=f4ffa217&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/gm6f2h9u\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fgm6f2h9u&h=c934adfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/6ypwuvxg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F6ypwuvxg&h=642b0343&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/3y7usxoi\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F3y7usxoi&h=866fae59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/cgxyqusj\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fcgxyqusj&h=0d96cc25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/r3bzpv51\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fr3bzpv51&h=8e2c6240&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n／一張一合如美功鐵路市集／<br />\n<br />\n鐵路市集是當時《畢業十年，如何集氣七人去旅行》Vlog旅程最深刻的景點，位於泰國曼谷旁邊的一鎮，最引人入勝是整個市場緊貼著鐵道路軌擺攤，當火車鳴笛駛進時，攤販熟練地把檔口暫時收摺起來，待火車駛開，又徐徐重新擴張，像跳躍的脈搏心臟一樣，一張一合。"},{"pid":"bb044e320d3b0f6edba64d8664e44ff960f06f4b","tid":546593,"uid":57013,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T04:32:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/d3kfvbmc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fd3kfvbmc&h=dd28c863&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/o6fczgpk\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fo6fczgpk&h=6b26ed4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n／星空閣樓不一定有星空／<br />\n<br />\n第一次到台中是2015年的一月，也是《帶住長老去旅行》的第一次行程（原片可以在YouTube搜尋「TravelWhenCry」訂閱觀看）<br />\n<br />\n曾在網上看遊記介紹過，在清境晚上入睡時看天窗滿目星星的景色，於是在清境的行程就加入了這個浪漫想像，訂了宿費不低的兩個晚上。<br />\n<br />\n當晚躺在大床上，有暖墊溫著，從天窗進入眼簾的只有滿佈夜空的密雲卻沒有星星，縱便如此，精緻的小木屋也留下了很深刻的印象，而且翌日清晨小天窗也補償了我一道破雲而出的日出曙光，展開了當時台中南投的第一個早上。"},{"pid":"eb7d549798f304bd4f45dd3813d5a6434caa1cb1","tid":546593,"uid":61697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T06:05:11.000Z","msg":"pai 好正 好想去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e8183e743f831eaa1bb59e4a6a33ffc9a3942ee","tid":546593,"uid":57013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T10:55:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/1zetwsbg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F1zetwsbg&h=23fda2a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【討論】／如何在異地旅行搭巴士？／<br />\n-<br />\n這是一個我經常思考的問題，今天我想請教一下大家。<br />\n因為韓文的字元難以辨別，而且公車下車站提示的訊息經常延出錯，上次到韓國釜山坐公車時，就算知道下車站名，也要長期開著Google Map GPS定位，以及同時數算著巴士停了多少個站來估計到站了沒。<br />\n試過幾次早了或遲了下車，一個人時還樂得寫意在異地到處亂走，但身邊帶著女朋友或者長老時，就變成了走冤枉路。<br />\n你們平時旅行時又有甚麼貼士？"},{"pid":"2c23433c81f6a848c51fbd6dfc85777c2ff3766d","tid":546593,"uid":57013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T10:25:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/neh6w410\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fneh6w410&h=bfddcb33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/2plzfey5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F2plzfey5&h=7606e740&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2017年10月末開展了Banff National Park的單車旅行，路綫由Canmore開始，省卻了Calgary往Canmore的100公里路。由Canmore往Banff的路途只有25公里，海拔上爬約300米，下斜100米，慢騎如我花了約3小時才抵達。圖為路途上一條楓樹並立的單車路，也是Legacy Trail的開始，在0度氣溫之下，黃葉紛飛，身上只有一支Ukulele、一個背包和一架單車，別有出走的味道，於是我決定了和朋友在路上一邊彈唱著陳綺貞的《旅行的意義》，一邊完成短短5日的騎行旅程。"},{"pid":"6e945122ac5822bcb833252d67e2cb3b5f63a586","tid":546593,"uid":57013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb7d549798f304bd4f45dd3813d5a6434caa1cb1","tid":546593,"uid":61697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T06:05:11.000Z","msg":"pai 好正 好想去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T14:51:15.000Z","msg":"喺好正！同曼谷好唔同，不過交通唔方便，自駕會方便啲"},{"pid":"92ae77256e36cd1acade648d487ddd0c5906af66","tid":546593,"uid":47971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e8183e743f831eaa1bb59e4a6a33ffc9a3942ee","tid":546593,"uid":57013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T10:55:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/1zetwsbg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F1zetwsbg&h=23fda2a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【討論】／如何在異地旅行搭巴士？／<br />\n-<br />\n這是一個我經常思考的問題，今天我想請教一下大家。<br />\n因為韓文的字元難以辨別，而且公車下車站提示的訊息經常延出錯，上次到韓國釜山坐公車時，就算知道下車站名，也要長期開著Google Map GPS定位，以及同時數算著巴士停了多少個站來估計到站了沒。<br />\n試過幾次早了或遲了下車，一個人時還樂得寫意在異地到處亂走，但身邊帶著女朋友或者長老時，就變成了走冤枉路。<br />\n你們平時旅行時又有甚麼貼士？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T14:53:50.000Z","msg":"好驚旅行搭巴士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw 點解呢到冇人留言嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3c657ccaa80dfb85b2dc557a8bda6b70394d7b1","tid":546593,"uid":61697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T11:56:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 推"},{"pid":"974b2ba7f92738eeeac855a0de7f3d515ec454a3","tid":546593,"uid":48762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T02:44:55.000Z","msg":"留名"}]}